2026-01-15 18:09:55,409 - INFO - Line : # The schema says bot:containsZone is for Locus of a Room. So Room is contained by Site.
2026-01-15 18:09:55,410 - INFO - Line : # bot:containsZone is for Zone -> Space. bot:Site is a Space. bot:Room is a Space.
