2026-01-15 18:10:00,401 - INFO - Line : bot:hasSpace bot:MainDataCenter . # bot:hasSpace is inverse of bot:containsZone, but bot:containsZone is for Zone -> Space. Room is a Space. Site contains Space.
2026-01-15 18:10:00,403 - INFO - Line : # The schema says bot:containsZone is for Locus of a Room. So Room is contained by Site.
2026-01-15 18:10:00,404 - INFO - Line : # bot:containsZone is for Zone -> Space. bot:Site is a Space. bot:Room is a Space.
